<template>
    <input type="checkbox" ref="checkbox" true-value="true" false-value="false" @change="didChange" />
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'CheckBox',
  props: {
  },
  methods: {
    didChange() {
        const checkbox = this.$refs.checkbox;
        const state = checkbox.value;
        this.$emit('change',state);
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>


</style>
